This is the default shield used by Mecha version `1.x.x`. I recommend you to use this shield as the base framework if you want to create a new shield for Mecha.

![1]([[asset]]/png/reference/shield/normal/1.png) {.align-center}

### Features

 - Automatic menu navigation
 - Automatic breadcrumb navigation
 - Automatic set the home page view to `article`
 - Widgets: tags (requires [tag][link:../extension/tag] extension), recent posts, related posts
 - Comments (requires [comment][link:../extension/comment] extension)
 - Manual post excerpt (requires to add `<!-- cut -->` to the post content)
 - Post formats: _HTML_, _Markdown_, _Quote_.